Author: paraphrasis
Text: I don't think (and I don't hope) that anyone is going to help you with this one.  Please don't start this habit. It's horrible, it will get worse, and you will regret that you ever got into it.   It might seem like an easy fix, but it's an easy fix that will ruin your life.
